lvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot; mce_style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: #141823; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;La vida es un reto, afróntalo;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot; mce_style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: #141823; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;la vida es un juego, juégalo,&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot; mce_style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: #141823; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;la vida es preciosa, cuídala;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot; mce_style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: #141823; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;la vida es riqueza, consérvala;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot; mce_style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: #141823; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;la vida es un misterio, descúbrelo.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot; mce_style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: #141823; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: rgb(20, 24, 35); font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot; mce_style=&quot;margin: 0px; color: #141823; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;La vida es una promesa, cúmplela;&lt;/p